data.name: pictureBox2.ToolTip
data.value:
This will automaticly randomize your "from" and "to" values. Always set values first before you check this checkbox!
If unchecked you can set everything normal/manual. Features that aren't automized are: Enemy LP Enemy Deck Enemy Hand My Deck My Hand
Thats because those values should always be set on your own. !!! Enemy Grave / Monster Destroyed /are synchronized with Attacks Made !!!
